tokenize

public static String[] tokenize(String[] annovalue)
Returns the value of an annotation as an array of Strings. If the annotation value is an empty array, or has more than one elements, then the same array is returned. If the array has only one empty element, then an empty array is returned. If the array contains only one string that is contained by other strings separated by commas, then this string is split to its constituent tokens it and an array with the tokens is returned.

Parameters:
annovalue -
Returns:
Returns an array of strings.
